  <scopecontent id="aspace_4f2ad1d0130bf85504d07a55ed9c4393">
    <head>Scope and Content Notes</head>
<p>This collection includes personnel cards for employees of Jones &amp; Laughlin's plant in south side Pittsburgh.  These cards include the worker's name, date and place of birth, nationality, race, and wage rate.  Payroll information for several departments within the works is also present.</p>  </scopecontent>
